ygData.subject: Battle in Unrest
ygData.msgSnippet: The battle for all that is good,rightious and blessed by Tunare continues unabaited in the Estate of Unrest. I have found some most excelent groups to fight
ygData.messageBody:
The battle for all that is good,rightious and
blessed by Tunare continues unabaited in the Estate of
Unrest. I have found some most excelent groups to fight
with this weekend,made level 23 saturday night. I have
discovered the pleasures of grouping with an Enchanter,that
was very knowledgeable.She helped the group take on
and kill many creatures that normaly have us running
for our lives to the nearest zone. I am here now only
because of the patch problems they'v been having of late.
I have uploaded a couple of my favorite screen
shots to my Yahoo Photo site if any of you want to
check them out at
<a href=http://briefcase.yahoo.com/bc/Yahoo_lowlap target=new>http://briefcase.yahoo.com/bc/Yahoo_lowlap</a> I hope to see you all online in Norrath.
